  <entry>
    <title>Hello World</title>
    <url>/2021/04/22/hello-world/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p>
<h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p>
<h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p>
<h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>docker</title>
    <url>/2021/04/23/docker/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Docker的安装与卸载"><a href="#Docker的安装与卸载" class="headerlink" title="Docker的安装与卸载"></a>Docker的安装与卸载</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`Docker的安装`</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 1、卸载旧版本</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo apt-get remove docker docker-engine docker.io containerd runc</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 2、需要的安装依赖</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo apt-get install \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">    apt-transport-https \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">    ca-certificates \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">    curl \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">    gnupg-agent \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">    software-properties-common</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<span id="more"></span>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 3、添加官方密钥</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo apt-key add -</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo apt-key fingerprint 0EBFCD88</span></span><br><span class="line">pub   rsa4096 2017-02-22 [SCEA]</span><br><span class="line">      9DC8 5822 9FC7 DD38 854A  E2D8 8D81 803C 0EBF CD88</span><br><span class="line">uid           [ 未知 ] Docker Release (CE deb) &lt;docker@docker.com&gt;</span><br><span class="line">sub   rsa4096 2017-02-22 [S]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 4、 设置镜像仓库</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo add-apt-repository \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">   <span class="string">&quot;deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu \</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">   $(lsb_release -cs) \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">   stable<span class="string">&quot;                       # 官方国外源</span></span></span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo add-apt-repository \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">   <span class="string">&quot;deb [arch=amd64] http://mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/ubuntu \</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">   $(lsb_release -cs) \</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">   stable<span class="string">&quot;                     # 阿里源</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 5、安装docker</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo apt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 6、启动docker</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> service docker start</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 7、测试 hello-world  == 验证安装成功</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo docker run hello-world</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">8、查看下载的hello world</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo docker images</span></span><br><span class="line">REPOSITORY    TAG       IMAGE ID       CREATED         SIZE</span><br><span class="line">hello-world   latest    bf756fb1ae65   12 months ago   13.3kB</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`Docker的卸载`</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 1、卸载依赖</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo apt-get purge docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">2、删除目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> sudo rm -rf /var/lib/docker</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="阿里云镜像加速"><a href="#阿里云镜像加速" class="headerlink" title="阿里云镜像加速"></a>阿里云镜像加速</h2><p>1、访问阿里云，进入镜像加速器模块<code>https://cr.console.aliyun.com/cn-hangzhou/instances/mirrors</code></p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/23/docker/1.png" alt="image-20210126141522434"></p>
<p>2、配置使用</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p /etc/docker</span><br><span class="line">sudo tee /etc/docker/daemon.json &lt;&lt;-&#x27;EOF&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;registry-mirrors&quot;: [&quot;https://dc1ymt2l.mirror.aliyuncs.com&quot;]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">EOF</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl restart docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Docker的常用命令"><a href="#Docker的常用命令" class="headerlink" title="Docker的常用命令"></a>Docker的常用命令</h2><h3 id="镜像命令"><a href="#镜像命令" class="headerlink" title="镜像命令"></a>镜像命令</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker images        <span class="comment">#查看下载的镜像</span></span></span><br><span class="line">	-a / --all     ：显示所有的</span><br><span class="line">	-q / --quiet   ：只显示ID</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 解释</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> REPOSITORY            镜像的仓库名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> TAG					镜像的标签</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> IMAGE ID			    镜像的id</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> CREATED               镜像的创建时间</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> SIZE				    镜像的大小</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker search        <span class="comment">#搜索镜像</span></span>    </span><br><span class="line">	--filter       通过STARS来过滤</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker pull [:tag]   <span class="comment">#下载镜像</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ docker rmi -f        <span class="comment">#删除镜像</span></span><br><span class="line">$ docker rmi -f $(docker images -aq)  <span class="comment">#删除全部镜像</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="容器命令"><a href="#容器命令" class="headerlink" title="容器命令"></a>容器命令</h3><h4 id="Docker运行的流程"><a href="#Docker运行的流程" class="headerlink" title="Docker运行的流程"></a>Docker运行的流程</h4><p><img src="/2021/04/23/docker/2.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker run [参数] image <span class="comment"># 创建容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line">	-d       后台方式运行</span><br><span class="line">	-it      使用交互方式，进入容器查看命令</span><br><span class="line">	-p       指定容器的端口</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> <span class="built_in">exit</span>                   <span class="comment">#停止并退出</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ctrl + P + Q 			 <span class="comment">#不停止退出</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker ps    		     <span class="comment">#列出正在运行的容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line">	-a                   #列出历史运行过的容器 </span><br><span class="line">    -q   				 #只显示容器的编号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker rm             <span class="comment">#删除容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line">	-f                 	#强制删除</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker rm -f $(docker ps -aq)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker start   		<span class="comment">#启动容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker restart        <span class="comment">#重启容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker stop           <span class="comment">#停止容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker <span class="built_in">kill</span>           <span class="comment">#强制停止容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker <span class="built_in">exec</span> -it       <span class="comment">#进入后台运行的容器，开启新的终端</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker attach -it     <span class="comment">#进入后台运行的容器，继续之前的终端</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker top           <span class="comment">#查看容器内部的进程</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker cp            <span class="comment">#将文件拷贝到主机上</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker commit        <span class="comment">#创建一个新的镜像</span></span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/2021/04/23/docker/3.png"></p>
<h3 id="Volumes"><a href="#Volumes" class="headerlink" title="Volumes"></a>Volumes</h3><p>docker的卷技术，将容器的目录挂载在Linux下。一句话：容器的持久化与同步操作。</p>
<h4 id="具名挂载和匿名挂载"><a href="#具名挂载和匿名挂载" class="headerlink" title="具名挂载和匿名挂载"></a>具名挂载和匿名挂载</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 匿名挂载</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker run -d --name nginx -v /etc/nginx nginx</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看数据卷列表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker volume ls</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">具名挂载</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker run -d --name nginx -v aNam_nginx:/etc/nginx nginx</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看具体的数据卷</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker volume inspect aNam_nginx</span></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">删除数据卷</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker volume rm aNam_nginx</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 指定路径挂载</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker run -it -v 主机目录：容器内目录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">数据卷容器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker run -d --name nginx --volumes-from nginx0 nginx</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="端口映射"><a href="#端口映射" class="headerlink" title="端口映射"></a>端口映射</h3><p>​    docker容器在启动的时候，如果不指定端口映射参数，在容器外部是无法通过网络来访问容器内的网络应用和服务的。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker run [参数] image <span class="comment"># 创建容器</span></span></span><br><span class="line">	-P         			 #随机映射</span><br><span class="line">	-p  				 #指定映射</span><br><span class="line">		ip:port:port    #容器端口映射在指定ip端口</span><br><span class="line">		ip::port        #容器端口映射在指定ip随机端口</span><br><span class="line">		port:port		#容器端口映射在主机指定端口</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker port           <span class="comment">#查看映射端口配置</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ip addr               <span class="comment">#查看容器ip</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">实例部署nginx</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 1、下载nginx镜像</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker pull nginx</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">2、查看下载的镜像</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker images</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">3、启动并进行端口映射</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> docker run -d --name nginx01 -p:3344:80 nginx</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">4、测试是否完成端口转发</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> curl localhost:3344</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
